{"symbol": "TMED9", "uniprot": "Q9BVK6", "protein_name": "Transmembrane emp24 domain-containing protein 9", "length": 235, "function": "Appears to be involved in vesicular protein trafficking, mainly in the early secretory pathway. In COPI vesicle-mediated retrograde transport involved in the coatomer recruitment to membranes of the early secretory pathway. Increases coatomer-dependent activity of ARFGAP2. Thought to play a crucial role in the specific retention of p24 complexes in cis-Golgi membranes; specifically contributes to the coupled localization of TMED2 and TMED10 in the cis-Golgi network. May be involved in organization of intracellular membranes, such as of the ER-Golgi intermediate compartment and the Golgi apparatus. Involved in ER localization of PTPN2 isoform PTPB", "ensembl_gene": "ENSG00000184840", "scores": {"selectivity": 0.1061, "protein_drug": 0.684, "rna_drug": 0.796}, "flags": {"surface": false, "enzyme": true, "mod_aso": true, "mod_sirna": false}, "details": {"nominated_modality": "ASO", "winning_axis": "RNA", "quadrant": "Both viable", "best_route": "small molecule", "sm_score": "0.873", "sirna_score": "0.693", "aso_score": "0.699"}, "modality": "ASO", "structure": "data/structures/TMED9.pdb", "pockets": [{"rank": 1, "druggability": 0.505, "volume": 291.2, "residues": [68, 80, 82, 83, 126, 128, 129, 132]}, {"rank": 2, "druggability": 0.237, "volume": 533.7, "residues": [37, 38, 63, 64, 65, 105, 106, 107, 140, 141, 142]}, {"rank": 3, "druggability": 0.223, "volume": 328.0, "residues": [18, 21, 22, 25, 26, 29]}], "links": [{"key": "uniprot", "label": "UniProt", "url": "https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb/Q9BVK6"}, {"key": "alphafold", "label": "AlphaFold", "url": "https://alphafold.ebi.ac.uk/entry/Q9BVK6"}, {"key": "opentargets", "label": "Open Targets", "url": "https://platform.opentargets.org/target/ENSG00000184840"}, {"key": "genecards", "label": "GeneCards", "url": "https://www.genecards.org/cgi-bin/carddisp.pl?gene=TMED9"}, {"key": "ensemb